<h2>Help & User Guide</h2>
<ol>
<li><b>Login:</b> Use your username and password to access the system.</li>
<li><b>Customers:</b> Go to <i>Customers</i> to add, edit, or delete customer accounts.</li>
<li><b>Items:</b> Use the Items page to manage item details if required.</li>
<li><b>Billing:</b> Open <i>Calculate Bill</i>, enter the account number and units, then print.</li>
<li><b>Logout:</b> Click Logout to end your session.</li>
</ol>
<p>For issues: contact your administrator.</p>
